metadata.name: Explorations WE #1
metadata.description:
The "Explorations" collection continues with the IQOS WE series.  The works resolve around the exploration of chaos transitioning between order and disorder, creating never ending harmony, dealing with nonlinear things that are impossible to predict or control.

Each work is inspired by the colors of the new IQOS WE Edition and its dynamic colors that will help bring the artists mural to life.
